            <title>[HBASE-1600] Multiple HBase clients to multiple indpendent HBase clusters from the same jvm should be allowed</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-1600</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;ZK quorum servers list is static in ZooKeeperWrapper and is coupled to zoo.cfg. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This prevents multiple clients from connecting to multiple distinct HBase clusters and requires zoo.cfg to exist on a cluster that needs to connect to a remote HBase cluster.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
